### ==========================================
### 认证模块 API 测试
### ==========================================

### 1. 正常流程：管理员登录
POST http://localhost:18081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "XiyuAdmin2026!"
}

### 2. 正常流程：普通用户登录
POST http://localhost:18081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "xiaowang",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. 边界：密码错误
POST http://localhost:18081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### 4. 边界：用户不存在
POST http://localhost:18081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nonexistent_user",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 5. 边界：空用户名
POST http://localhost:18081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "",
  "password": "XiyuAdmin2026!"
}

### 6. 边界：空密码
POST http://localhost:18081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": ""
}

### 7. 边界：缺少必填字段
POST http://localhost:18081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 8. 未认证访问（无 Token）
GET http://localhost:18081/api/tenders?page=0&size=10

### 9. 无效 Token
GET http://localhost:18081/api/tenders?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token_here
